{"tid":207571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電騙停不了】26歲港大女生中招 損失71萬人民幣","createTime":"2017-04-19T03:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T04:38:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b0fd617a82fd576741e5cb632a660f854f2cea","tid":207571,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"一名26歲姓郭、就讀港大的內地女子，本月16日收到一名不明女子來電，對方自稱入境處人員，指她涉嫌干犯刑事罪行，電話及後轉駁到另一名男子，對方聲稱為內地執法人員，要求她匯款至一銀行戶口。女子不虞有詐，依其指示先後五次匯款共約71萬元人民幣，但其後懷疑受騙遂報案。<br />\n<br />\n經初步調查後，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由西區警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56582621&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56582621%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170419&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=02eeb1fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56582621%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170419&h=374f6e3c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56582621&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170419</a>"},{"pid":"99599f8c3edaccd1765d3a9e859449b0541d6f87","tid":207571,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:30:15.000Z","msg":"開頭睇完，心諗讀得港大都咁蠢？完來係強國人，唔怪得之啦！"},{"pid":"d6f02e9415ba5b30623f088cd1dc8b83875eb94b","tid":207571,"uid":28887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"肯撚定身有屎"},{"pid":"115bccfcb8872311831d5325a042bfdc4373cb71","tid":207571,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:32:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d72e6296040132865663ea86231d869deb0c5ae","tid":207571,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:35:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾標題<br />\n支那女生就支那女生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d437a72974037463b33b7751eb79d5ab5f5905","tid":207571,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>內地生，26歲 好多洗黑錢，，身有屎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係，點會只係呃內地生，又唔見港豬出事？</blockquote><br />\n這邊廂比錢佢幫手洗黑錢<br />\n那邊廂扮公安呃佢錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}